Wiimotedev Project Changelog
============================

1.3
- IS HIGHLY RECOMMENDED FOR ALL 1.2 USERS
- added powersave mode feature
- integration with wiimotedev-register
- integration with wiimotedev-client
- integration with wiimotedev-toolkit
- integration with wiimotedev-examples
- integration with wiimotedev-uinput
- integration with qwiimotedev
- better compatibilty with wiimotedev-client
- important cleanups and optimalisations in core code
- fixed various bugs
- process of registration new wiiremote(s) should be easier with wiimotedev-register

1.2
- First public release
- Support for streaming wiiremote events by network
- Support for local dbus interface (org.wiimotedev.daemon)
- Added init.d script for debian, gentoo, slackware, ubuntu
- Added to org.wiimotedev.deviceEvents

Methods:
  bool dbusIsClassicConnected(quint32 id)
  bool dbusIsNunchukConnected(quint32 id)
  bool dbusIsWiimoteConnected(quint32 id)
  quint32 dbusWiimoteGetAverageLatency(quint32 id)
  quint32 dbusWiimoteGetBatteryLife(quint32 id)
  quint32 dbusWiimoteGetCurrentLatency(quint32 id)
  quint8 dbusWiimoteGetLedStatus(quint32 id)
  quint8 dbusWiimoteGetStatus(quint32 id)
  QList < uint> dbusGetWiimoteList()
  QStringList dbusGetUnregistredWiimoteList()
  bool dbusWiimoteGetRumbleStatus(quint32 id)
  bool dbusWiimoteSetLedStatus(quint32 id, quint32 status)
  bool dbusWiimoteSetRumbleStatus(quint32 id, bool status)

